lists in swimming]]\n[[Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming]]\n[[Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in open water swimming]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the FINA World Swimming Championships (25 m)]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2008 Summer Olympics]]\n\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games gold medalists for Tunisia]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games silver medalists for Tunisia]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2001 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2005 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2009 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2013 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:African Games gold medalists for Tunisia]]\n[[Category:African Games medalists in swimming]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games medalists in swimming]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2003 All-Africa Games]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Tunisian swimmer}}\n{{Infobox swimmer|\n| name           = Oussama Mellouli\n| image          = Oussama Mellouli 2013.jpg\n| imagesize      = 200px\n| fullname       = Oussama Mellouli\n| native_name    = \u0623\u0633\u0627\u0645\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0648\u0644\u064a\n| nicknames      = The Mediterranean's Shark, Ous\n| nationality    = {{TUN}}\n| height         = 1.92 m\n| weight         = 84 kg\n| strokes        = Free, IM\n| club           = {{flagicon|Tunisia}} [[Esp\u00e9rance Sportive de Tunis|Esperance of Tunisia]]\n| collegeteam    = [[USC Trojans]] <small>(USA)</small>\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1984|2|16}}\n| birth_place    = [[La Marsa]], Tunisia\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| medaltemplates = \n{{MedalCompetition | [[Swimming at the Summer Olympics|Olympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalGold | [[Swimming at the 2008 Summer Olympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Swimming at the 2008 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 1500 metre freestyle|1500 m freestyle]]}}\n{{MedalGold | [[Swimming at the 2012 Summer Olympic