 of 2020]]\n*[[List of Gaon Album Chart number ones of 2020]]\n*[[List of Gaon Digital Chart number ones of 2020]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Refbegin}}\n*{{note label|Single|1||The following was released as a single but charted on the [[Gaon Album Chart]].}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{K-pop}}\n\n[[Category:2020 in South Korean music]]\n[[Category:South Korean music]]\n[[Category:K-pop]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Dynamic list}}\n{{YYYY music|2020}}\n{{Year nav topic5|2020|South Korean music}}\nThe following is a list of notable events and releases that have happened, or are expected to happen in 2020 in music in [[South Korea]].\n\n==Debuting and disbanding in 2020==\n===Debuting groups===\n{{Further|List of South Korean idol groups (2020s)#2020}}\n<!--Artists must have their own article to added to the list and must be sourced-->\n* [[B.O.Y]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=112&aid=0003234099|title=\uae40\uad6d\ud5cc-\uc1a1\uc720\ube48, 2\uc778\uc870 \uadf8\ub8f9 \ube44\uc624\ube0c\uc720(B.O.Y) \uc0c8 \ucd9c\ubc1c\u2025\uc5ed\ub300\uae09 \u7537\ub4c0\uc624 \ud0c4\uc0dd[\uacf5\uc2dd]|work=entertain.naver|date=November 12, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[DKB (band)|DKB]]<ref name=\"DKB\"/>\n*[[MCND]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/018/0004547572|title=\uc2e0\uc778 \uadf8\ub8f9 MCND, \ud504\ub9ac \ub370\ubdd4 \ud6c4 \uc74c\uc6d0 \ubc1c\ub9e4 '\ub0a8\ub2e4\ub978 \ud589\ubcf4'|date=2020-01-02|website=entertain.naver|access-date=2020-01-02}}</ref>\n* [[UNVS]]<ref name=\"UNVS\">{{cite web|last1=Yu|first1=Byeong-cheol|script-title=ko: UNVS(\uc720\uc5d4\ube0c\uc774\uc5d0\uc2a4), \ub370\ubdd4 \uc2f1\uae00 'Timless' \ubc1c\ub9e4\u2026\uac10\uc131 \ud37c\ud3ec\uba3c\uc2a4\ub3cc' \ub3c4\uc57d \uc704\ud55c \uccab\uac78\uc74c|url=http://news.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202002240025|website=[[Korea Economic Daily|Korea Economic Daily TV]]|publisher=Korea Business News Company|accessdat